# Allowed source IPs/CIDRs for inbound HEC (8088) and S2S (9997).
# Copy to nsg-allowed-sources.conf to override the default (0.0.0.0/0).
#
# One address or prefix per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Default (when this file is missing or empty): 0.0.0.0/0 — all sources.
# For production on-prem access, replace with your egress IP(s) or VPN CIDR, e.g.:
# 203.0.113.50
# 10.20.0.0/16

